      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 41 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 41 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>損，有孚，元吉，无咎，可貞，利有攸往。曷之用？二簋可用享。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In (what is denoted by) Sun, if there be sincerity (in him who employs it), there will be great good fortune:--freedom from error; firmness and correctness that can be maintained; and advantage in every movement that shall be made. In what shall this (sincerity in the exercise of Sun) be employed? (Even) in sacrifice two baskets of grain, (though there be nothing else), may be presented.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
