      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 41 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 41 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：已事遄往，无咎，酌損之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject suspending his own affairs, and hurrying away (to help the subject of the fourth line). He will commit no error, but let him consider how far he should contribute of what is his (for the other).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
