      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 41 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 41 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：利貞，征凶，弗損益之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows that it will be advantageous for its subject to maintain a firm correctness, and that action on his part will be evil. He can give increase (to his correlate) without taking from himself</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
