      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 41 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 41 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：三人行，則損一人；一人行，則得其友。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows how of three men walking together, the number is diminished by one; and how one, walking, finds his friend.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
