      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 41 六四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：損其疾，使遄有喜，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject diminishing the ailment under which he labours by making (the subject of the first line) hasten (to his help), and make him glad. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
