      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 41 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：或益之，十朋之龜弗克違，元吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows parties adding to (the stores of) its subject ten pairs of tortoise shells, and accepting no refusal. There will be great good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
